---
import Layout from '~/layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '~/components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '~/components/Footer.astro';

export const prerender = true;
---

<Layout title="Refund and Cancellation — Nexigrate" description="Nexigrate's refund and cancellation policy." pathname="/refund">
  <Nav />
  <main id="main" class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 py-16 sm:py-20">
    <p class="pill mb-5">Refund</p>
    <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight text-ink-900 sm:text-5xl">
      Refund and Cancellation Policy
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-muted-500">
      Effective date: 23 May 2026 · Currency: Indian Rupee (₹).
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10 space-y-8 leading-relaxed text-ink-800">
      <p>
        We want every paying student to feel that the upgrade was worth it.
        If you don’t, we will refund you. Read the rules below before you pay
        so we’re both on the same page.
      </p>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-ink-900">1. Free plan</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          The Nexigrate free plan stays free. No charge, no refund needed.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-ink-900">2. 7-day refund window</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          For our paid plans (Scholar, Aspirant, Achiever — monthly or yearly),
          you can request a full refund within <strong>7 calendar days</strong>
          of the payment date for any reason, no questions asked, as long as:
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6">
          <li>You have not consumed more than 25% of the plan’s included
              mock tests; and</li>
          <li>You have not exported or shared more than 100 MCQ
              explanations.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">
          The thresholds exist so the refund window cannot be used as a free
          one-week trial of the paid tier.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-ink-900">3. Pro-rated refunds for yearly plans</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          If you cancel a yearly subscription after the 7-day window, you can
          ask for a pro-rated refund of the unused months, minus a 10%
          processing fee. We do not pro-rate monthly subscriptions; they end
          at the close of the period you paid for.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-ink-900">4. Service issues</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          If the Service is materially broken — extended outages, persistent
          incorrect content, or a feature you specifically paid for stops
          working — we will refund the affected period in full regardless of
          the timing rules above. Email us with the date and a short
          description of the problem.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-ink-900">5. How to request a refund</h2>
        <ol class="mt-3 list-decimal space-y-2 pl-6">
          <li>
            Email <a class="text-ember-600 underline" href="mailto:hello@nexigrate.com">hello@nexigrate.com</a>
            from the email address registered on the account.
          </li>
          <li>
            Include the Razorpay <em>payment ID</em> from your receipt
            (starts with <code>pay_</code>).
          </li>
          <li>
            One line on what went wrong (helps us improve, and is mandatory
            for service-issue refunds).
          </li>
        </ol>
        <p class="mt-3">
          We acknowledge within 2 working days and process eligible refunds
          within 5–7 working days. The refund returns to the same payment
          method (UPI, card, netbanking) used for the original charge. Bank
          processing times may add another 3–5 business days.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-ink-900">6. Cancellation</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          Subscriptions do not auto-renew. You don’t need to cancel to stop
          being billed; you simply don’t renew. To delete your account
          entirely, see the deletion section of our
          <a class="text-ember-600 underline" href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-ink-900">7. Disputes</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          If we can’t agree on a refund, the <a class="text-ember-600 underline" href="/terms">Terms of Service</a>
          dispute and jurisdiction clauses apply. Please raise a chargeback
          only as a last resort — chargebacks cost both of us money and time
          we’d rather spend on the product.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-ink-900">8. Contact</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          Questions about a refund or cancellation:
          <a class="text-ember-600 underline" href="mailto:hello@nexigrate.com">hello@nexigrate.com</a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
